text: Lajas de Tolé is a corregimiento in Tolé District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 847 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 906; its population as of 2000 was 850. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
